headline: Exxon Restarts Key Gasoline Unit After Brief Beaumont Refinery Outage
summary: ExxonMobil has restarted the gasoline-producing fluid catalytic cracking unit (FCCU) at its massive Beaumont, Texas, refinery, two days after an unexpected shutdown temporarily disrupted operations
